No prob, Ryo.

::Killfest/EndBringer/Scyther/Incarcinator/Greven/Demise::

Killfest manuevers out of the way of the plasma shots, catching one in 
the arm but recieving almost no damage. He looks at Dark, aiming his 
EMP rifle. Killfest fires three shots from the rifle, followed by two 
signature-seeking missiles at Dark.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
His scanners detecting firepower, EndBringer spins around, placing Koj 
in the way of Liono's blast.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Cloaked from view and scanners, Scyther flies into the battle. Knowing 
that firing would give away his position (as well as his presence), he 
takes out his scythe, flying silently toward Dark's back.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Incarcinator smiles, looking at the battle. Its been a long time.

"Its nice to be back, Commander," he says to Killfest over the 
terrorists' internal communication system. Its been a while since he'd 
fought alongside Killfest.

Incarcinator aims his rifle at Inu, firing three very-high-speed, 
explosive shells. The kickback sends him flying back a bit, but his 
jetpack equals it out and keeps him mostly stational.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Tired of waiting for a reply, Grimmler taps in a few commands on the 
console of the shuttle he and Demise were in. The shuttle launches 
off, heading toward the battle in space.
